---
title: Pasta Parmesan with Bell Pepper, Tuscan Herbs & Marinara Sauce
description: Pasta in tomato sauce can be a fantastic feast—it just needs a few accents to take it beyond basic. Luckily, we’ve got some good ones. This penne in marinara comes with bell pepper, Tuscan herbs and spices, a cheesy breadcrumb crust, and a drizzle of basil oil. Once you’ve tossed everything together and popped it in the oven, you’re just minutes away from cheesy, herbaceous, saucy, and just ever so slightly spicy bliss.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pasta-parmesan-1e85f2c5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pasta-parmesan-5df00ee653520b7ca92f2a99-8b35e6d2.pdf
